body_html:
The CPU type that gets built for in Android Studio/Gradle builds is defined here: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/examples/android/build.gradle#L10

The default is armeabi-v7a, so if you're running in an x86 emulator you'll need to change that accordingly.

The CPU type that gets built for in Android Studio/Gradle builds is defined here: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/examples/android/build.gradle#L10

The default is armeabi-v7a, so if you're running in an x86 emulator you'll need to change that accordingly.
